{"id":156226,"date":[{"year":1949,"month":7,"day":19}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"360","ytitle":"","mtitle":"为你空出一把椅子","ftitle":"——一多先生遇难三周年","authors":["臧克家"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北平解放了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜爱北平的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到他们的北平来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的北平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在等待着你呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待着你的归来!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北平解放了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘文代大会’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里开得真热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七百多个名字里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找不到你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，你的勇敢，你的牺牲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是多响亮的一个提议!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘新政协’也快要开会了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不同党派的人士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不同的地方聚拢来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来得那么踊跃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结得这样坚实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在未来的会议席上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该为你空出一把椅子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一个知识份子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又是一个勇猛的斗士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你丢弃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真舍得!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你接受，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真澈底!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不是‘一夜得道’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明早醒来，魔高一丈，道高一尺!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你呼喊:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘呵，人民!’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民，在毛泽东的旗子下翻了身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民决不会忘记你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们把对你对敌的战斗里!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，你热爱它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也曾为它的不争气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追胸号啕过；的感激"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表现在　　今天，对着新的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追胸哭泣了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为它丧失了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最忠贞的一个儿子!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三八，七月八日"}]}